     <target>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.1	Gap analysis on existing risk information in the Kofirnighan River Basin conducted
Technical documents on procurement of automated weather stations in the most vulnerable 
1.2	districts of the Kofirnighan River Basin prepared
1.3	Initial consultations with local stakeholders on catchment strategy development held.
1.4	Review of existing mechanisms on catchment management.
1.5	Particular PES to be identified
2.1 Preparatory activities for ToT conduction to be completed
2.2. Mapping of the watershed conditions to be conducted
2.3 Preparatory activities for EbA interventions to be completed
3.1 Mapping of existing knowledge management platforms on climate change conducted.
3.2 The Impact Evaluation Framework to be partially established/tested</narrative>
      </comment>
     </target>
     <actual>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.1 The Gap analysis is initiated and ongoing
1.2 Draft technical procurement documents are prepared
